latestIgtvVideos.title: Makeup Quickie 👅
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I've tried to create a minimal glam look you can put anywhere anytime without feeling too loud. As we all are stuck at home, I put on my experiment gloves to take advantage of this situation. The key is to practice. I hope you enjoy watching it✨
P.S~ I'm not a professional, I'm still learning my way out.
.
The Products Used are:
🦋 Wet and Wild Photo Focus Concealer in the shade Medium Tawny.
🦋 L.A. Girl Pro Conceal HD in the shade Light Ivory.
🦋 Becca Ignite Liquified Highlighter in Passion.
🦋 Hoola Bronzer 
🦋 Bobbi Brown Pot Rouge in Rose.
🦋 Huda Beauty Mercury Retrograde Palette in the shade Karma for a natural background.
🦋 Huda Beauty Mercury Retrograde Palette in the shade Off Balance for the nude pink touch.
🦋 Huda Beauty Mercury Retrograde Palette in the shade Gold Glitch to top it off with glam.
🦋 Nude Kohl for waterline.
🦋 Mascara by Flower Beauty.
🦋 Kay Beauty Lip Liner in the shade Sensational.
🦋 Maybelline New York Matte Liquid Lipstick.
🦋 Makeup Revolution Soph X Highlighter.
🦋Topping it up with The BodyShop Face Mist for a natural dewy skin.
.
